# =============================================================================
# LangChain + MCP Tutorial - Environment Variables
# =============================================================================
#
# This project uses FREE APIs! Here's what you need:
#
#   1. OpenAI API Key (REQUIRED) - For the LLM
#   2. NewsData.io API Key (OPTIONAL) - For news tools (free tier: 200 req/day)
#   3. Open-Meteo - NO KEY NEEDED! 100% free!
#
# SETUP:
#   1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
#   2. Fill in your API keys below
#   3. Run: python agent_main.py
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit your .env file! It's in .gitignore.
